  "prompt": "How long does it take an iStockphoto photography contributor application to be processed?",
  "response": "The processing time for an iStockphoto photography contributor application can vary, but it typically takes between a few days to a couple of weeks. The review process involves evaluating the quality and style of the submitted samples to ensure they meet iStock's standards. If it takes longer than a couple of weeks, it might be worth reaching out to their support team for an update. Keep in mind that response times can also depend on the volume of applications they are processing at any given time.",
